t\u016bponotanga: Te ine i te tupono ka puta he kaupapa
w\u0101hi tauira: Ko te huinga o nga putanga katoa ka taea o te whakamatautau tupono
takahanga: He huinga putanga ka tautapahia he tūponotanga
putanga: He hua ka taea e te whakamatautau tupono
toharite: Tapeke o nga uara kua wehea ki te maha o nga uara
whakam\u0101tautau matap\u014dkere: He tukanga e kore e mohiotia te putanga kia kitea ra ano
taea: He kaupapa karekau he tupono ka puta
matap\u014dkeretia: Ka whakahaerehia e te whai waahi riterite ranei mo ia mea
